text: Cnut cyngc gret Eadsige biscop & ælfstan abbot & ægelric & ealle mine þegenas on Cent freondlice.

& ic cyðe eow þæt ic hæbbe geunnan æþelnoðe arcebisceope ealre þare landare þe ælfmær hæfde & mid rihte into Cristes cyricean gebyrað binnan birig & butan on wuda & on felda swa full & swa forð swa ælfric arcebiscop hyre weold oþþe ænig his forgengena.
